Package: AddFonts
Title: Add Fonts from Several Providers to 'showtext'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Guillaume", "Noblet", , "gnoblet@zaclys.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Download and register fonts from several providers for use in R graphics 
    with the 'showtext' package. Currently supports Bunny Fonts (<https://fonts.bunny.net/>), 
    a privacy-focused alternative to Google Fonts. Functions are designed similar to 
    'font_add_google()' with extensible architecture for additional font providers.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
